Thanks, Alexander!

I realised that could have described the problem and the solution better.

There are actually two problems:

* MarkupEditor blocks Ctrl+PgUp/PgDn, because that key combo is used by CTabFolder to switch its internal tabs. This makes the default next/previousTab bind unusable so it is hard to navigate away fro a MarkupEditor using the keyboard.
* MarkupEditor does not handle the next/previousSubTab commands. Instead it depends on the build-in CTabFolder for switching between source and preview tabs.

This commit fixes the problems by these changes:

* Ctrl+PgUp/PgDn tab switching is disabled in CTabFolder.
* A command handler is added for the next/previousSubTab commands. This is the new way for switching between source and preview tabs.
